## Removed from Watch List
- certifi (Python): truststore is ecosystem-endorsed replacement, default in pip 24.2+.
- xeipuuv/gojsonschema (Go): google/jsonschema-go and santhosh-tekuri/jsonschema cover this.
- spf13/cast (Go): Released v1.10.0 Sept 2025, actively maintained.
- go-ini/ini (Go): Already covered by stanza.
- colorama (Python): Already covered by chromapaint.
- minimist (Node): Alternatives exist (util.parseArgs, yargs-parser, mri).
- tabulate (Python): Actively maintained as of March 2026 (astanin merging PRs).
- patrickmn/go-cache (Go): Now stash project.
- Rust ecosystem: Most unmaintained crates have community forks.

